cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.HC 

The paper discusses the application of machine learning and deep learning models for the prediction of epileptic seizures using EEG data. This falls under the domain of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC) as the models are trained on medical data and aim to improve the diagnosis and treatment of epilepsy.
